<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٩٧ - <span class="c2">(١٧٨٦)</span> وَحَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3057">عَاصِمُ بْنُ النَّضْرِ التَّيْمِيُّ </a>، حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6257">مُعْتَمِرٌ </a>قَالَ: سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2609">أَبِي </a>، حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5183">قَتَادَةُ </a>قَالَ: سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسَ بْنَ مَالِكٍ</a> <span class="c2">(ح)</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>